Non-Disclosure Analysis
 ├─ Data Ingestion & Integration
 │   ├─ Tables & Key Joins
 │   │   ├─ DIM_PJ_CASE ↔ DIM_PJ_LIFE (via SID)
 │   │   ├─ DISCLOSURE_DF_PUDB ↔ DIM_PJ_LIFE (via Life ID)
 │   │   └─ DIM_PJ_EA_LABS_DETAIL ↔ DIM_PJ_LIFE (via FK_LIFE_DIM_PJ_SID)
 │   ├─ Master Identifier (Case ID, Life ID, SID)
 │   └─ Data Quality (missing values, duplicates, consistent formats)
 │
 ├─ Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
 │   ├─ Structured Fields (demographics, coverage, lab values)
 │   ├─ Textual Fields (disclosure answers, doctor notes)
 │   └─ Correlation (declared vs. lab evidence, mismatches)
 │
 ├─ Feature Engineering
 │   ├─ Structured Features (age, gender, underwriting flags)
 │   ├─ NLP Features (keyword flags, LLM-based classification)
 │   ├─ Discrepancy Features (mismatch flags, risk scores)
 │   └─ Time-Based Features (date/time of tests, diagnoses)
 │
 ├─ NLP & LLM Strategy
 │   ├─ Preprocessing & Labeling (tokenization, domain dictionaries)
 │   ├─ Summarization & Classification (LLM-based)
 │   └─ Entity Recognition (medical terms, ICD codes)
 │
 ├─ Predictive Modeling
 │   ├─ Supervised Classification (labels: non-disclosure likely)
 │   ├─ Anomaly Detection (isolation forest, autoencoders)
 │   └─ Explainability & Compliance (SHAP, LIME)
 │
 ├─ Deployment & Workflow Integration
 │   ├─ Integration with Underwriting Systems (risk flags)
 │   ├─ User Feedback Loop (underwriters’ verifications)
 │   └─ Monitoring & Maintenance (model drift, retraining)
 │
 └─ Future Enhancements
     ├─ Active Learning (human-in-the-loop)
     ├─ Knowledge Graphs (conditions, symptoms, labs)
     └─ Speech-to-Text (if interview recordings available)
